{
  "text": "The cation leak appears, to some extent, to be reproduced upon heterologous expression of the human HsRhAG variants in xenopus oocytes [CITATION_1] . Of note, the leak was not only induced by the F65S variant but also by expression of native HsRhAG. Activities of endogenous Na + ,K + -ATPase and Na",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "5109610"
